286
00:22:48,400 --> 00:22:51,559
Guard Geng? Who's Guard Geng?

287
00:22:52,380 --> 00:22:55,539
He was a guard in our family, and his name is Geng Zhi.

288
00:22:55,539 --> 00:22:57,179
I brought him here quite often before.

289
00:22:57,179 --> 00:22:59,599
