298
00:23:16,900 --> 00:23:18,960
Is that him?

299
00:23:18,960 --> 00:23:19,960
Oh, it is!

300
00:23:19,960 --> 00:23:20,839
You know what?

301
00:23:20,840 --> 00:23:22,580
He's quite weird!

302
00:23:22,580 --> 00:23:24,939
He always came at the busiest hour!

303
00:23:24,939 --> 00:23:26,979
And he always asked for our most-wanted girl!

304
00:23:26,979 --> 00:23:29,719
He'd sit in the accountant room waiting for a long time!

305
00:23:29,720 --> 00:23:30,879
And he kept talking to me!

306
00:23:30,880 --> 00:23:34,161
But I was so busy and I didn't have the time to talk to him!

307
00:23:51,979 --> 00:23:53,259
Isn't he weird?

308
00:23:53,259 --> 00:23:55,540
