355
00:29:15,359 --> 00:29:17,359
If it's necessary,

356
00:29:17,939 --> 00:29:19,839
I will see it as a threat, too!

357
00:29:21,340 --> 00:29:23,720
It's not the first day you've known me.

358
00:29:24,780 --> 00:29:26,278
I've known about the specific location of Su's Manor.

359
00:29:26,279 --> 00:29:28,219
If you don't say yes,

360
00:29:30,259 --> 00:29:32,479
I'll kill your whole family!

361
00:29:36,960 --> 00:29:40,080
I don't believe you would do such a thing!

362
00:29:40,080 --> 00:29:45,740
Just like you believe that I wouldn't eliminate your whole camp.

363
00:29:53,219 --> 00:29:55,579
I know a threat won't work on you.

364
00:29:59,599 --> 00:30:01,520
So let me beg you!

365
00:30:02,240 --> 00:30:04,419
I just want you to help me think of an idea to save my Master!

366
00:30:04,419 --> 00:30:05,659
I only need an idea!

367
00:30:05,659 --> 00:30:06,919
You don't need to show up or participate in it!

368
00:30:06,920 --> 00:30:09,100
There will be no trouble at all!

369
00:30:09,100 --> 00:30:12,359
Even if we fail, we won't sell you out!

370
00:30:18,820 --> 00:30:22,820
Brother Fan, Fang Tian Lei killed Qian Xi Wen,

371
00:30:22,820 --> 00:30:25,100
connived in Bao Wen Han's evil doings,

372
00:30:25,100 --> 00:30:28,820
and killed so many innocent citizens in Lin'an.

373
00:30:28,820 --> 00:30:31,160
According to the law of the Wu Dynasty,

374
00:30:31,160 --> 00:30:32,758
he should be beaten on his back

375
00:30:32,759 --> 00:30:35,060
and suffer a thousand cuts until death.

376
00:30:35,060 --> 00:30:38,140
But I did ask the Secret Investigation Department

377
00:30:38,140 --> 00:30:41,479
to write a letter to ask for mercy to the Emperor.

378
00:30:41,480 --> 00:30:43,959
Given that Bao Wen Han is dead

379
00:30:43,959 --> 00:30:46,839
and Badao Camp contributed to the relief distribution.

380
00:30:49,160 --> 00:30:51,640
The Emperor won't torture him.

381
00:30:51,640 --> 00:30:54,179
He will only be decapitated in public.

382
00:30:57,319 --> 00:30:59,060
There are some things that must not be done.

383
00:30:59,060 --> 00:31:03,560
I can't help you with this.

384
00:31:05,319 --> 00:31:06,820
I know it's difficult for you!

385
00:31:06,820 --> 00:31:10,760
But nothing changes even if you sacrifice all you have!

386
00:31:11,440 --> 00:31:13,800
Your Master has violated the national law

387
00:31:13,800 --> 00:31:15,819
and hurt so many citizens!

388
00:31:15,819 --> 00:31:18,380
