392
00:31:30,400 --> 00:31:33,140
But if you do that,

393
00:31:33,140 --> 00:31:35,560
not only will Dong Dao Fu and I stop you,

394
00:31:35,560 --> 00:31:40,398
but also the tens of thousands of citizens who became homeless because of him!

395
00:31:42,119 --> 00:31:45,999
I know and understand what you said!

396
00:31:45,999 --> 00:31:47,699
But he's my Master after all,

397
00:31:47,699 --> 00:31:51,019
and also Liu Xi Gua's uncle who brought her up.

398
00:31:51,019 --> 00:31:53,480
He's like our father!

399
00:31:54,279 --> 00:31:56,559
How can we just leave him alone?

400
00:31:58,459 --> 00:32:01,140
I owe you two my life.

401
00:32:01,140 --> 00:32:03,579
Without the two of you,

402
00:32:03,579 --> 00:32:06,720
I would've long been dead under the sword of Bao Wen Han.

403
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:08,540
So,

404
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:13,739
I'll do everything to protect you

405
00:32:17,140 --> 00:32:18,940
and Xi Gua.

406
00:32:19,820 --> 00:32:25,259
Actually, Xi Gua understands what you just said.

407
00:32:25,259 --> 00:32:27,620
She just can't hate you,

408
00:32:28,540 --> 00:32:30,600
but she doesn't want to see you, either.

409
00:32:34,659 --> 00:32:36,860
That's how she is.

410
00:32:37,519 --> 00:32:40,520
Saving Master is now her priority.

411
00:32:40,520 --> 00:32:44,079
She'd even do it alone.

412
00:32:47,620 --> 00:32:51,799
Ning Yi, she can't be hurt.

413
00:32:51,799 --> 00:32:55,538
Actually, she shouldn't have gotten herself involved in this matter in the first place.

414
00:32:55,538 --> 00:32:58,700
Could you please write a letter and help me to persuade her?

415
00:32:58,700 --> 00:33:01,579
I know it might not work out, but…

416
00:33:05,079 --> 00:33:07,399
You already knew I'd come to you?
[To Xi Gua]

417
00:33:07,399 --> 00:33:09,539
Deliver this letter to her.

418
00:33:15,100 --> 00:33:16,259
I'm leaving.

419
00:33:16,259 --> 00:33:18,479
- Let me see you out.
- Just leave me here.

420
00:33:21,739 --> 00:33:25,559
You are concerned about our nation. I can't question it.

421
00:33:25,559 --> 00:33:29,280
